Name = "Trickshot"
Category = 1
Description = "Release a kinetic projectile at your enemy dealing %Damage damage to enemies or restoring %Healing health to allies.

At the end of the bullet's travel it ricochets in any direction of your choice.

$Infuse (1): Give the projectile $Piercing (2), but also increase cooldown of this ability by 1 turn."
